<!-- ============ QUESTIONS / FAQ ============ -->
<section class="band" id="questions">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="band-head center reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">Questions?</div>
      <h2>The things every owner <em>asks first.</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <details class="faq reveal"><summary>Do I have to switch my practice management software? <span class="pm"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#211F1B" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></span></summary><div class="ans">No, and that's the whole point. WhiskerBeacon sits on top of the tools you already run, whether that's Avimark, Cornerstone, ezyVet, Vetspire or something else. We wire what you have into one system. Nothing gets ripped out.</div></details>
      <details class="faq reveal"><summary>Is the free agent actually free, or is it a trial? <span class="pm"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#211F1B" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></span></summary><div class="ans">Genuinely free, and yours to keep. We build Scout, our missed-call and after-hours agent, fully functional and wired into your setup, and she stays working whether or not you ever buy anything else. No expiry, no crippled features, no card required.</div></details>
      <details class="faq reveal"><summary>Will AI be making medical decisions about my patients? <span class="pm"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#211F1B" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></span></summary><div class="ans">No. We stay strictly in the front office and back office: booking, reminders, follow-ups, recall, charge checks. Diagnosis, dosing and every clinical call stays with your team. We won't go near the exam room.</div></details>
      <details class="faq reveal"><summary>How long does a build take? <span class="pm"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#211F1B" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></span></summary><div class="ans">Scout, your free agent, lands in days. The full crew in WhiskerPack is a short, fixed-scope build, not a months-long project. You'll see something working quickly, because the work itself is the proof.</div></details>
      <details class="faq reveal"><summary>What does it actually cost? <span class="pm"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#211F1B" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg></span></summary><div class="ans">Scout is free. WhiskerPack, the whole crew, starts at $499 a month to keep running. WhiskerShadow, for multi-site or complex setups, starts from $6,000 plus monthly. Against a clinic's monthly revenue, the build pays back fast when it recovers even a handful of lapsed patients.</div></details>
